title: Stephanie Farmer
text:
Hi! I’m Steph, a third-year Ecosystem Science and Sustainability student at Colorado State University. I’m passionate about integrating sustainability into industries to create a more resilient future. Outside of academics, you’ll find me exploring the outdoors—whether it’s hiking, camping, or simply appreciating nature. I’m always eager to learn, connect, and make a positive impact!
